				      		<p>SQL Statement, Data manipulation language(DML): Select, Insert, Update,Delete,etc Data Definition language(DDL):Create, Alter, Drop,Rename, Comment etc.Data Control language(DCL): Grant, Revoke etc.Transaction Control. Retrieving Data Using the SQL SELECT Statement,Basic Select Statement, Selecting All Columns, Selecting Specific Columns etc.</p>
